(4, 'Dolphin Encounter ', '&lt;p&gt;A program for &lt;strong&gt;all ages&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;strong&gt;Learn and have fun!!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Discover the dolphin&amp;acute;s best-kept secrets in a safe and fun-filled environment.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Make a friend for a lifetime!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;You will be surprised by the great inteligence and friendliness of these wonderful marine mammals.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;You will also have the opportunity to hug it, kiss it, let it kiss you on the cheek and enjoy watching your new friend while it performs a series of amazing behaviors.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;They will make you tingle with excitement!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This program is ideal for children...of all ages.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;From Cancun to Isla Round Trip Ferry&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;From Riviera Maya to Pto.Aventuras Ground Transportation Round Trip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Dolphin Encounter (kiss, hug, hand target, picture with ball, peck shake, free time)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;15 guests per group to swimm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Beverage on board (sodas and water)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Visit to Isla Mujeres Down Town&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Watch sharks and stingray&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'US$5 p/p Dock Fee\r\nPhoto and video\r\nTips and Souvenirs\r\nTurtle Farm visit ($30 pesos)', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Register&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Ferry leave at 9:00 am&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;aprox 30 min to Isla Mujeres&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Briefing and Instructions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;40 min Dolphin Encounter&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Free time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;5:30 pm return to Canc&amp;uacute;n&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'DAILY', '&lt;p&gt;** pregnant women and children under 1.20 mts&amp;nbsp; &lt;strong&gt;could do the activity with an adult paid and signing a responsive&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Meeting Point:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n