(5, 'Sky Rider', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Sky Rider experience will take you up!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;up and away into the clear blue &lt;strong&gt;Caribbean&lt;/strong&gt; Sky.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Sit back and gaze at the impressive sights of the sea, lagoon and Cancun hotel zone.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;This unique mechanism provides a &lt;strong&gt;comfortable&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;secure ride &lt;/strong&gt;as you are lifted from a platform on the back of the boat.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Bottled Water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Life jacket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'US$3 Dock fee payable upon check-in.\r\nGround Transportation (call us and ask for a quotation).', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Departs every half hour from 9 am until 4:30 pm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Register&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;enjoy the best view!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'MONDAY TO SATURDAY', '&lt;p&gt;Meeting Point: &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Aqua World (Boulevard Kukulc&amp;aacute;n Km. 15 + 300. Int. Marina Aquaworld. Canc&amp;uacute;n Hotel Zone)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kids under 11 years US$33 with a paying adult.&lt;/p&gt;', '0.00', '0.00', NULL, NULL, 'sky-rider', 2, 'images/pictures/560642.jpg', 1, NULL, '0', '1', 'Sky rider | cancun tours | cancun sightseeing | skydive Caribbean			', 'cancun sightseeing,tour cancun,skydiving tours,skydive,skydive caribbean,excursions in cancun,cancun sightseeing tours,sightseeing cancun,tours to cancun,skydiving caribbean.', 'Take a ride on our SkyRider.Two people can enjoy the heights of the Cancun Sky in complete safety and comfort.Would you like to be dunked? You just need to ask.', '1'),
(6, 'Aquatwister', '&lt;p&gt;Your ride involves massive sideways slides, wave riding and the famous &lt;strong&gt;&quot;Powerbrake Stop&quot;&lt;/strong&gt; in which the jet boat comes to a complete stop within two boat lenghts, not forgetting of course the incredible &lt;strong&gt;270&amp;ordm; spins.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AWESOME!!!!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #0000ff;&quot;&gt;**Prepare to get wet **&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Bottled Water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Life Jacket&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'US$3 Dock fee payable upon check-in.\r\nGround Transportation (please call and ask for a quotation)', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Register&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Briefing and instructions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;feel the adrenaline!!&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'MONDAY TO SATURDAY', '&lt;p&gt;**Do not allow pregnant women and kids under 1.20 mts or 7 years old.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Meeting point: &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Boulevard Kukulc&amp;aacute;n Km 6.5 Int.Marina Aqua Tours. Canc&amp;uacute;n Hotel Zone&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Times: 11 am, 12 pm, 1, pm or 2 pm&lt;/p&gt;', '0.00', '0.00', NULL, NULL, 'aquatwister', 2, 'images/pictures/662924.gif', 1, NULL, '0', '0', 'Aquatwister  | cancun tours | cancun adventures', 'jet boat,jet boating,shotover jet,shotover jet boat,jungle tour cancun,water in cancun,cancun adventure,shotover jet boating,adventures in cancun,boats cancun', 'Feel the adrenaline running through your body, on this mountain rusaacuatica. Feel the waves in these unexpected tunnels.', '1'),
(7, 'Camel Safari', '&lt;p&gt;Enjoy a 2 hour journey through the exotic jungle of the Riviera Maya in our beautiful camels.&lt;br /&gt;Be part of this unique adventure, in the middle of the way, you will find an oasis to catch you bread, relax and enjoy delicious fresh fruits and water.&lt;br /&gt;The journey begins at the &lt;strong&gt;Marina Maroma&lt;/strong&gt;, which is located in the heart of the Riviera Maya.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;There will find your camel and bigins your magicla journey in the heart of the Mexican Caribbean.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Will go through the jungle and beach area (dunes)&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Fresh bottle water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Fresh Fruit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Ground Transportation Round Trip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Photos and Video/Souvenirs/Tips', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Pick up at your hotel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Arrive at Camel Ranch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Choose your camel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Start the adventure&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'MONDAY TO SATURDAY', '&lt;p&gt;** Do not allow pregnant women and kids under 1.20 mts.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Meeting Point: Camel Ranch / Pick up at your Hotel Lobby&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Times: 09:00 am, 12:00 pm and 03:00 pm&lt;/p&gt;', '77.00', '70.00', NULL, NULL, 'camel-safari', 25, 'images/pictures/772285.gif', 2, NULL, '0', '1', 'camel safari | camel cancun  | cancun tour', 'camel safari cancun,camel cancun,cancun tours,tours from cancun,tours a cancun,the mayan riviera,cancun tour,jungle tours,cancun excursion,camel safari', 'This tour is completely different, an amazing experience alongside these unique friend. This tour was designed to enjoy the hypnotic waters of the Caribbean.', '1'),
(8, 'Rio Secreto', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Natural Treasure!!!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Rio Secreto invites you on a fantastic voyage, a magical journey that will bring to life your amazing sensory adventure.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Discover the secrets of a real &lt;strong&gt;underground river&lt;/strong&gt;, the longest and most spectacular of the region; travel into another world of extraordinary beauty.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Learn and marvel in this ancient, magical subterranean world that until now has remained unexplored for millions of years.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;You be guided on a &lt;strong&gt;one and a half hour (or 600 mts) Tour of Rio Secreto&lt;/strong&gt;, walking and swimming along the route.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;A Light but a substantial lunch will be enjoyed after this unique and exciting experience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Equipment for all activities,&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Ground Transportation from Cancun-rio-Cancun&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;entrance fees&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;towels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;meals and beverages&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', ' Ground Transportation from Cancun Hotels (please call us and ask for a quotation)/Photo and Video/Souvenirs\r\nTips', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Verdana&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;sans-serif&amp;quot;; font-size: 7.5pt;&quot; lang=&quot;ES-MX&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Verdana&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;sans-serif&amp;quot;; font-size: 7.5pt;&quot; lang=&quot;ES-MX&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Verdana&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;sans-serif&amp;quot;; font-size: 7.5pt;&quot; lang=&quot;ES-MX&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst&quot; style=&quot;line-height: normal; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; mso-add-space: auto; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: