ted to an extraordinary world, making it the largest and most spectacular river of the region.', '1'),
(9, 'Paradise Horseback Riding', '&lt;p&gt;The most natural and relaxed way to enjoy the jungle. You will be thrilled with the wildlife.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Ground Transportation Round Trip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Tax&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;local medical insurance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Beverage (sodas and water)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;beans and chips&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'Souvenirs/Photo and Videos/Tips', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Pick up at your Hotel Lobby&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Briefing and instructions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;choose your horse&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;and feel the breeze&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'MONDAY TO  SATURDAY', '&lt;p&gt;Meeting Point: Pick up at your Hotel (please confirm your pick up time with your Tour Agent)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Times: 09:30 am, 12:00 pm and 03:00 pm&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '77.00', '70.00', NULL, NULL, 'paradise-horseback-riding', 25, 'images/pictures/j5phn5bminihbm.jpg', 2, NULL, '0', '1', 'Paradise Horseback Riding | horse riding vacations | horse riding', 'horseback riding cancun,horseback rides,horse riding vacations,horse riding adventures,tours in cancun,best tours in cancun,cancun horseback riding,horseback riding in cancun,horse riding cancun,horse riding in cancun', 'The more relaxed way to enjoy the flora and fauna, with a 2 hour full contact with Mother Nature. Is a tour that you can enjoy with family and friends.', '1'),
(10, 'Tulum Express', '&lt;p&gt;Tulum is located aproximately &lt;strong&gt;south of Cancun&lt;/strong&gt;, at 1hr and 30min from Cancun and 40min to Playa del Carmen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Not only is the largest coastal archaelogical site in Mexico, is one of the corners of the Caribbean where you can still enjoy the lush &lt;strong&gt;nature&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;discover the intersting history &lt;/strong&gt;of it. &lt;strong&gt;Tulum means &quot;Wall&quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is the best and most famous example of east coast style, the name by which designates the architectural type of Mayan buildings constructed on the north coast of Quintana Roo between 1200 and 1520 AD. Their structures, including the Castle and the Temple of the Frescos, notable for their preservation and for the high quality of the murals still preserved inside both.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;As the most extensively studied, both in appearance and in the ethnohistorical archeology, visiting Tulum is fundamental to understanding the life and customs of the Maya who lived during the Postclassic period in Quintana Roo.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Here you can find: &lt;strong&gt;Culture, attraction, fun, tranquility and a lifetime experience&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;A/C Bus&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Entrance Ruins&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Tour guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', ' Train ride at tulum ($25 pesos)', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Departure from Cancun&amp;nbsp; 8:30am&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Arrival to Tulum&amp;nbsp;10:30am&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Departure from Tulum 1:00pm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Arrival from&amp;nbsp;Cancun 3:00pm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'MON / WED / FRI', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pick up place&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;at the Capitan Cove unique departure at 8:30am. Blvd. Kukulcan Km 16.5 Hotel Zone&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Please Bring:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;comfortable walking shoes and clothe&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Biodegradable sunblock&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Biodegradable repellent&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Swim suit on&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Hat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Cash for Souvenirs and Tips&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '57.00', '41.00', NULL, NULL, 'tulum-express', 9, 'images/pictures/1011582.png', 5, NULL, '0', '1', 'Tulum express | tulum express tour | tulum ruins	', 'tulum ruins,tulum express,tulum tours,tulum mayan ruins,tulum ruins,mayan ruins,tours tulum,tulum express tour,mayan ruins of tulum,dolphins swimming with.', 'Enjoy Mayan culture one of the best views of the Mexican Caribbean,as well as swimming in one of the most beautiful beaches and return to your hotel. ', '1'),
(11, 'WET&#039;N WILD', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The fun park in Cancun, where you will find water slides, wave pool, space for kids and the whole family will enjoy even more in this paradise of white sand and turquoise water.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;We have:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #0000ff;&quot;&gt;Wave Pool&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;: where you can enjoy constant waves and lots of fun.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Depth without waves: 0 to 2.40 m / 0-8 ft.&lt;br /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Depth with waves: 0-3 m / 0-9 ft.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff0000; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Lazy River&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: enjoy our river of 300 meters in length in its crystalline waters and quiet in the comfort of a tire ....&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Length: 320 meters, width: 4.40 m, depth: 94 cm (3 fts)&lt;br /&gt;(Not including rental / tire: $ 4 - $ 10 usd deposit)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #0000ff;&quot;&gt;Double Space Bowl: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;slip from 15 meters in height, for a fun slide to more than 50 km / h run ends with a refreshing dive.&lt;br /&gt;* Height: 10.10 m, Length: 39.40, Depth: 3 mts. 9 feet&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #ff0000; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Bubba Tub&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: fun for the whole family, have fun on 6 floors of fun, sharing the journey on a giant wheel will take you through gullies and a refreshing surprise landing.&lt;br /&gt;* Height: 16.25 meters, length: 85 meters, depths: 1.25 m, 4 feet&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #0000ff; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Bumper Boats&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: New attraction for little ones, inflatable boats, enjoy a small naval battle.&lt;br /&gt;