(12, 'Xcaret Full Day', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Xcaret&lt;/strong&gt; is a magical paradise where culture, &lt;strong&gt;ecology&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Mexican&lt;/strong&gt; wildlife meet. Among its great &lt;strong&gt;treasures&lt;/strong&gt;, in Xcaret we can find &lt;strong&gt;Underground Rivers&lt;/strong&gt;, a &lt;strong&gt;Butterfly Pavilion&lt;/strong&gt;, a &lt;strong&gt;Beach&lt;/strong&gt;, Inlets and Xcaret&amp;rsquo;s one of a kind &lt;strong&gt;celebration &amp;ldquo;Xcaret Mexico Espectacular&amp;rdquo;. &lt;/strong&gt;At Xcaret you can enjoy the &lt;strong&gt;most amazing water activities &lt;/strong&gt;such as swimming with dolphins, snuba, sea trek and snorkeling.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&quot;Xcaret&quot; means small inlet in Maya&lt;/strong&gt;, because it has an inlet of extraordinary beauty. Geographically convenient location of this cache made attractive to the Maya, who built a port there and commercial center. Its old name was &#039;Pole&#039;, derived from the root p&#039;ol, which means merchandise and try to traders.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;A/C Bus R/T Transportation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Entrance to Xcaret&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Tour guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Park Xcaret Night Show&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Map&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'Lunch and beverage/optional activities/ lockers and towels/ snorkeling equipment/\r\ndinner during the show at night', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Departure from Cancun 10:00am&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Arrival to Xcaret and tour guide 11:15am&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Meeting point for night show&amp;nbsp;6:30pm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Departure from Xcaret 9:30pm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Arrival to Cancun 10:40 to 11:00pm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'DAILY', '&lt;p&gt;Please Bring:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Comfortable shoes and clothing &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;biodegradable sunblock&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;biodegradable&amp;nbsp;mosquito repellent&lt;/li&