(15, 'Tulum Xel-Ha All Inclusive ', '&lt;p&gt;Tulum is located approximately &lt;strong&gt;south of Cancun&lt;/strong&gt;. At 1hr and 30min. from Cancun and 40min to Playa del Carmen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;the perfect combination between a cultural visit not to far a way and water activities in the beatifull blue lagoon of Xel-ha.&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Tulum means &quot;Wall&quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is the best and most famous example of east coast style, the name by which designates the architectural type of Mayan buildings constructed on the north coast of Quintana Roo between 1200 and 1520 AD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;A/C Bus&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Entrance at Ruins&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Tour guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Park Xel-Ha All Inclusive&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', ' Swim with Dolphin and optional activities. Park Xcaret Night Show, Chikin-Ha Kantenah.', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Departure from Cancun 8:15am&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Arrival to Xel-Ha 9:45am&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Departure from Xel-Ha 2:30pm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Arrival to Tulum 2:45pm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Departure from Tulum 4:45pm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Arrival to Cancun 6:30pm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'DAILY', '&lt;p&gt;Bring:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Comfortable shoes &amp;amp; clothe&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;biodegradable sunscreen&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;biodegradable insect repellent&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;camera&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;extra money for shopping&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '159.00', '79.50', NULL, NULL, 'tulum-xel-ha-all-inclusive-', 8, 'images/pictures/1527369.png', 5, NULL, '0', '1', 'Tulum Xel-Ha All Inclusive  | tulum xel-ha tours | tours xel ha', 'tulum xel-ha tours,tulum xel-ha all inclusive excursion,tulum mayan ruins tours,tulum xel ha all inclusive,tulum excursion,tours xel ha,xel ha tours,xel ha mayan riviera,xel ha mayan,xel-ha park', 'is a unique experience where you know about the most important culture of the region, and relax in natural spa is fantastic around the world.', '1'),
(16, 'Paradise ATV &amp; Speed Boat', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Combine a perfect land and sea day full of fun.&amp;nbsp; Your tour begins when you arrive at the spectacular Maroma Beach in the Riviera Maya, considered to be one of the top beaches in the world by independent reviewers, including Travel Discovery Channel.Our friendly staff will welcome you to Marina Maroma Paradise and offer a brief explanation about your ATV and Speedboat tour.&amp;nbsp; Then, head toward the starting point and drive your Paradise ATV through tropical scenery full of action and speed.&amp;nbsp; Spend 45 minutes on a four wheel ATV; you will be in control of your own vehicle with a professional guide to lead the way through the terrain and jungle paths.&amp;nbsp; Ride past secret white sand dunes, a magical wilderness with stunning views.&amp;nbsp; Hold on tight!&amp;nbsp; Teens and adults will have a great time.After your ATV time is up, return to the starting point in Marina Maroma Paradise, and head to the beach to continue the adventure;&amp;nbsp; as you board your speedboat for more fun.&amp;nbsp; Feel the rush of adrenaline as you drive your own speedboat through crystal clear waters along the magnificent coast.&amp;nbsp; Breathe in the fresh breeze and glide in curves and in straight directions toward the marvelous beach landscapes of Maroma Bay.&amp;nbsp; Spend 45 minutes behind the wheel of your speedboat and head back to the starting point.&amp;nbsp; At the finish line you can use the beach facilities of Marina Maroma.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Equipment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Ground Transportation Round Trip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;tax&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;local medical insurance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;soft drinks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;beans and chips&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'US$2 Federal Marine Park and dock fee payable upon check in.', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Register&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Briefing