(20, 'Paradise ATV &amp; Wave Runner', '&lt;p&gt;Drive your &lt;strong&gt;4 wheels ATV &lt;/strong&gt;trough the jungle for &lt;strong&gt;45 &lt;/strong&gt;minutes and &lt;strong&gt;enjoy mother nature &lt;/strong&gt;at its best after that, Drive your own &lt;strong&gt;wave runner &lt;/strong&gt;for &lt;strong&gt;25&lt;/strong&gt; minutes over the Caribbean sea and let the adrenaline take you to total &lt;strong&gt;freedom&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Equipment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Ground Transportation Round Trip&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Tax&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;local medical insurance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;soft drinks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;beans and chips&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'US$2 Federal Marine Park and dock fee payable upon check in.', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Register&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Briefing and Instructions&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;ATV&amp;acute;s 45 minutes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Waverunner 25 minutes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Refreshments and snacks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'Mon to Sat', '&lt;p&gt;Meeting Point: &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Marina Maroma High way Can&amp;uacute;n -Tulum Km 55 Riviera Maya&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;ATV &amp;amp; Wave Runner available on sharing or single occupancy.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Single Unit &lt;/strong&gt;Price per Adult US$115&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shared Units &lt;/strong&gt;Price per Adult US$100&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kids under 17 &lt;/strong&gt;with a paying adult as a companion US$70&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Do not allow kids under 10 years&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '0.00', '0.00', NULL, NULL, 'paradise-atv-and-wave-runner', 25, 'images/pictures/y2o5wvbminiatvwr.jpg', 2, '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Single Unit Price per Adult US$115&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Shared Units Price