(21, 'Xel-Ha All Inclusive', '&lt;p&gt;The park is centered around the natural inlet and lagoon, which is promoted as one of the main attractions of the park that forms with the flow of the river through rocks mixing salty waters with fresh underground water currents.&lt;br /&gt;Xel-H&amp;aacute; considered the largest aquarium in the world where hundreds of species inhabit; such as tropical fish and an abundant flora. In the park there is also a turtle reserve, and butterfly reserve,&amp;nbsp;where research is constantly carried out to learn more about marine life and contribute with the ecological maintenance of the area.&lt;br /&gt;the public is permitted to swim and snorkel in the lagoon. Underwater the limestone has been eroded into a myriad of small caves and grottos.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;A/C Bus&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Tour guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Entrance to The Natural Wonder&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Beverages and food for 8 hrs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Towels&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Lockers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Bicycle&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Hiking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Hiking&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Pick up from&amp;nbsp;the hotel at 7:00am&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Arrival at Xel-Ha at 10:00am approx&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Activities&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Free time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Arrival to Cancun at 6:oopm approx&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '', 'DAILY', '&lt;p&gt;Comfortable shoes and clothing, swim suit, biodegradable sunscreen, mosquito repellent, hat and money for shopping.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Snorkeling equipment, towel and locker&amp;nbsp;(USD$20 deposit)&lt;/p&gt;', '139.00', '69.50', NULL, NULL, 'xel-ha-all-inclusive', 8, 'images/pictures/2103555.png', 5, NULL, '0', '1', 'Xel-Ha All Inclusive | xel ha all inclusive | xel-ha park ', 'tours xel ha,xel ha t