(22, 'Ek Balam - Hubiku - Aldea Maya', '&lt;p&gt;This Tour was designed for all&amp;nbsp;that loved of the naturale&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;this tour is perfect to know the Riviera Maya and to enjoy with the&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Family.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;*A/C Bus&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Entrance to Ek Balam Zone&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Breakbfast in the bus&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Entrance to Ecologic Park Hubiku&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Buffet Lunch&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Visit to Valladolid for 30min.&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, '&lt;p&gt;Departure from cancun arround 8:15 and arriving at Ek Balam at 10:15.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;going to Ecologic Park and visit the Cenote in Hubiku&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;after that lunch in the restaurant Aldea Maya to be there untill 13:00 hrs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;going to Valladolid 30min. and getting back to&amp;nbsp;Cancun at 17:30&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Tuesday- Thursday', '&lt;p&gt;*Shoes and Clothing Comfortable&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Repelent Mosquito&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Sunscreen block&lt;/p&gt;', '139.00', '109.00', NULL, NULL, 'ek-balam-hubiku-aldea-maya', 9, 'images/pictures/2210909.gif', 2, NULL, '0', '1', 'Ek Balam - Hubiku - Aldea Maya', NULL, NULL, '1'),
(23, 'Mayan Xtreme', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Be a part of&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;nature&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;as you experience the most thrilling adventure ride. Blend yourself in a perfect mixture of adventure &amp;amp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;nature&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;. Fly 20 meters (60 feet) above the jungle&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;canopy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;on the fastest zip line ride in the region! Test your tenacity as you rappel 21 meters (70 ft) down into the mayan jungle. Afterwards, wind down and snorkel in the mystical waters of an underground river with crystal clear waters and astounding rock formations. Delight yourself by sampling real Mexican cuisine as a perfect finish.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;* Transportation in air-conditioned van&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Professional bilingual guide&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* snorkeling &amp;amp; climing equipment&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Prescription mask available on request&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Lunch &amp;amp; beverages&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Insurance&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Taxes&lt;/p&gt;', '* Photos\r\n* Tips', '&lt;p&gt;Pick up lobby at 7:30&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;tour estimate time 6 hr&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Basic swimming skills required.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;This&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;tour&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is not suitable for people with severe physical or motor handicap, serious heart problems, or people who are not able to handle moderate physical activity.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Children under the age of 6 may participate under the responsibility and direct supervision of a responsible parent or family member.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;People under the influence of alcohol or drugs will not be permitted to participate in this&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;tour&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Comfortable clothes and footwear&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Water shoes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Sunglasses and a hat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Bathing suit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Extra T-shirt and&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Towel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BIODEGRADABLE sunscreen and mosquito repellent&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '0.00', '0.00', NULL, NULL, 'mayan-xtreme', 29, 'images/pictures/2357246.gif', 2, NULL, '0', '2', 'mayan-xtreme', NULL, NULL, '1'),
(24, 'Mayan Adventure', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Live a wonderful jungle and ocean experience, discover in one day three extraordinary ecosystems of the Mayan world. Surprise yourself with&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mexico&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;acute;s biodiversity and join us in the snorkeling&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;tour&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;that will change your way of feeling&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;nature&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;. We will dive into the turquoise waters of the mexican&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;caribbean&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;surrounded by exotic marine life; explore an underground river in the middle of the jungle, and discover the mystical wonders of the mayan sinkholes (cenotes). We will pick you up and drop you off at your&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hotel Lobby&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;and you will be accompanied at all times by our professional guides, that will share with you the best snorkeling techniques and information regarding the flora and fauna that inhabits this unique ecosystems. Above all they will make sure you feel safe and enjoy an unforgettable snorkeling experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;* Transportation in air-conditioned van&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Professional bilingual guide&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* snorkeling &amp;amp; climing equipment&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Prescription mask available on request&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Lunch &amp;amp; beverages&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Insurance&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;* Taxes&lt;/p&gt;', '* Photos\r\n* Tips', '&lt;p&gt;Pick up lobby at 7:30&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;tour estimate time 6 hr&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Everyday', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Basic swimming skills required.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;This&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;tour&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is not suitable for people with severe physical or motor handicap, serious heart problems, or people who are not able to handle moderate physical activity.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Children under the age of 6 may participate under the responsibility and direct supervision of a responsible parent or family member.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;People under the influence of alcohol or drugs will not be permitted to participate in this&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;tour&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Comfortable clothes and footwear&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Water shoes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Sunglasses and a hat&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Bathing suit&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Extra T-shirt and&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Towel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BIODEGRADABLE sunscreen and mosquito repellent&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Extra cash (tips, pictures).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '0.00', '0.00', NULL, NULL, 'mayan-adventure', 29, 'images/pictures/9025657.jpg', 2, NULL, '0', '2', 'Mayan adventure Riviera Maya', NULL, NULL, '1'),
(25, 'Columbus Lobster Dinner Cruise', '&lt;p&gt;Did you run out of ideas to show love to your partner? ... Nothing compares to the lobster dinner in Columbus, aboard a 60-foot Spanish galleon.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;In Cancun you have two options for this incredible and romantic tour diner:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;the beat of a live saxophone and under a sunset, almost as beautiful as the moments you&amp;acute;ll spend next to the person that you love. In our Galleon Columbus, while the sunsets behind the darkness of the night, the colors of the sky once again ignite the flame of love ..&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Or the second option: if you need moments of romance and tenderness with your partner, this option under the moonlight and stars. Aboard our Galeon Columbus, the melodies of a live saxophone and the gentle movement of the lagoon will make you remember how important love is and how perfect it would be if shared with the right person.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Revive love and enjoy one of the best nights of your life!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Columbus Cruise is for couples only!.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Open Bar with a glass of wine or champagne toast&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Gourmet Dinner (Surf &amp;amp; Turf)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Sax lived Music&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'Ground Transportation (please call and ask for a quotation)/Photos ', '&lt;p&gt;Summer Time: 5:30 pm or 8:30 pm&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Winter Time: 5:00 pm or 8:00 pm&lt;/p&gt;', 'MONDAY TO FRIDAY ', '&lt;p&gt;Meeting Point: &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Boulevard Kukulk&amp;aacute;n Km 6.5 Int. Marina Aqua Tours. Canc&amp;uacute;n Hotel Zone.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Recommendations: Casual Wear, photo camera, cash and comfortable shoes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Minimum age: 14 years old.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Duration: aprox 3 hours&lt;/p&gt;', '0.00', '0.00', NULL, NULL, 'columbus-lobster-dinner-cruise', 3, 'images/pictures/6aonzc1vg2fpaminicolumbus.jpg', 1, NULL, '1', '3', 'columbus lobster dinner cruise | lobster dinner cruise | cancun cruise', 'columbus lobster dinner cruise,romantic lobster dinner,lobster dinner cruise,lobster cruise,columbus cruise,lobster dinner,relaxing cruise,columbus cancun,cancun lobster,cancun dinner cruise', 'If you are looking for is to light the flame of love again this tour is perfect to tell him or her how much you love. This tour was made especially for lovers', '1'),
(26, 'Paradise Subsee', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Can be combined with Paradise Snorkel for a complete adventure &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Paradise Sub See explore the astounding Punta Nizuc reef from the comfort of the &lt;strong&gt;yellow submarine&lt;/strong&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;First we&#039;ll take you on an exciting boat ride through the mangrove jungle of the lagoon.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Upon to the reef site, you board the &lt;strong&gt;Sub See Explorer &lt;/strong&gt;for your magical underwater ride.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Bottled&amp;nbsp; water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Round trip to platform for board the Sub See for you magical underwaterride.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Lockers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Lunch back&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'Dock Fee of US$5 payable upon check-in, Ground transportation (please call us and ask for you quotation).', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Registrer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;On Aquaworld take boat to move to the platform&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Arriving at the platform, do the activity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Back to Aquaworld&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'MONDAY TO SATURDAY', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meeting Point:&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt; Boulevard Kukulcan Km. 15+300. Int. Marina Aquaworld. Cancun Hotel Zone&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Departures: Every hour from 9am til 3pm&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Minimum age: No age limit&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kids under 11 years $ 22usd&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Total time tour: 2 hrs&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ride time: 30 min&lt;/p&gt;', '0.00', '0.00', NULL, NULL, 'paradise-subsee', 2, 'images/pictures/2623897.gif', 1, NULL, '0', '1', 'Paradise Subsee | cancun snorkeling tours | cancun aquaworld			', 'cancun snorkeling tours,subsee paradise,cancun aquaworld,aquaworld in cancun,fish in cancun,adventures in cancun,snorkeling in cancun,snorkel tours,cancun snorkeling,cancun trips.