(27, 'Paradise Ocean Safari', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;the fare for unit is: Adult 104 usd and Chld 84 usd&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;the fares above are for share units.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pilot your wave runner &lt;/strong&gt;for 50 minutes and &lt;strong&gt;snorkel at the second largest reef of the world &lt;/strong&gt;for an aditional 50 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Enter in contact with the underwaterworld, at the best location of the Mayan Caribbean &amp;iexcl; 2 hours of &lt;strong&gt;Extreme Adventure &lt;/strong&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Equipment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Round trip transportation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Tax&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Local medical insurance&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Soft drinks&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Water&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Beans and chips&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', ' Reef conservation fee US$7 per person at your register.', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Pick up at your hotel lobby&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;if you stay at Hotel in Riviera Maya or Playa del Carmen the pick up is at your Hotel Lobby&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Register in Marina Maroma&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;choose your wave runners (Enjoy&amp;nbsp;for 50 minutes then Snorkel for more 50 minutes).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Free time&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Lunch (beans and chips)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Back to your hotel&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'MONDAY TO SATURDAY', '&lt;p&gt;Meeting point in Cancun: &lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Boulevard Kukulcan Captain Cove 16.5 km Hotel Zone (in front&amp;nbsp;The Omni Hotel)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Please Bring&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;comfortable shoes and clothe&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;swimming gear&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;camera&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;extra cash for tips, pictures, souvenirs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Aditional Service: Lockers, restaurants, bathrooms, medical service, 