(45, 'Paradise Snorkel Cancun', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Enjoy unlimited snorkeling fun on our Paradise Snorkel from a floating platfom for as long as you wish.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our bilingual guides will supervice and guide you round the area and make sure you don&#039;t miss anything. Punta Nizuc reef is a natural garden of bright coral and is home to an abundance of fish and other marine life.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Round trip to Paradise Platform&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Unlimited guided snorkel tour&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Beer and refreshmens aboard the Paradise Platform&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Snorkel equipment&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Lunch back&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', ' \r\nDock Fee of US$5 payable upon check-in\r\nGround transportation (please call us and ask for a quotation)', '&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Registrer&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;On Aquaworld take boat to move to the platform&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Arriving at the platform, do the activity&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Back to Aquaworld&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;', 'MONDAY TO SATURDAY', '&lt;p&gt;Meeting Point:&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt; Boulevard Kukulcan Km. 15+300 Int. Marina Aquaworld. Cancun Hotel Zone&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Departures: Every hour from 9am til 3pm&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kids under 11 years US$22&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '0.00', '0.00', NULL, NULL, 'paradise-snorkel-tour', 2, 'images/pictures/vyz2gpkminisaw.jpg', 1, NULL, '0', '1', 'paradise snorkel tour cancun', NULL, 'Unlimited guided snorkeling tour,In Punta nizuc reef is a natural garden of bright coral,abundance of fishes and other marine life,guides are bilingual.', '1'),
(46, 'Extreme Canopy Adventure', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Our excursion begins with pick up at the lobby of each hotel, once all our guests are onboard; our journey begins towards the community of Central Vallarta, where our park is located, just 40 Minutes away from Cancun or Playa del Carmen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;comic sans ms&#039;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Upon arrival, all guests are greeted at the &amp;ldquo;Casa Zatara&amp;rdquo;; this unique &amp;ldquo;palapa&amp;rdquo; offers W/C, restaurant, bar, lockers in a beautiful jungle ambiance. Our first activity will be the &lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;Extreme Canopy Tour&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;. In order to do this our staff will equip each guest with harnesses, security pulleys, helmets and gloves, our personnel will be in charge that all equipment is properly fitted.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;comic sans ms&#039;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;comic sans ms&#039;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Thrill seekers are welcome to experience THE NEXT LEVEL! Selvatica&amp;rsquo;s Extreme Canopy Tour is set upon our &amp;ldquo;EXTREMO&amp;rdquo; circuit, zip lining on 12 cables faster and in the middle of the jungle. Since security is a fundamental part of our park, precise instructions will be given on how the activity must be performed, so adventure may safely begin.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The next step is to ride one of our military trucks &amp;ldquo;Pinzhauer&amp;rdquo; into our open cenote &amp;ldquo;Lukuma&amp;rdquo;, swim and refresh yourself, while experiencing our custom water zip line, splashing right in the middle of the sinkhole; ride back to our &amp;ldquo;palapa&amp;rdquo; where complimentary lunch and water will be served, Photos, videos, snacks and souvenirs available on our premises.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: &#039;Maiandra GD&#039;,&#039;sans-serif&#039;; mso-fareast-font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;; mso-bidi-font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;; color: #003300; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ES; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Round transportation, Extreme Canopy Tour, Military Trucks, swim in the cenote, light lunch and drinks.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Tips\nPictures\nDVD\nAlcoholic Drinks', '&lt;p&gt;Daily&lt;/p&gt;', 'DAILY', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Restrictions: No pregnant women, back pains, or heart problems, maximum weight260 Lbs., maximum waist size47 in.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Maximum capacity: 60 pax per tour.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '99.00', '49.00', NULL, NULL, 'extreme-canopy-adventure', 18, 'images/pictures/9388731.JPG', 2, NULL, '0', '1', 'extreme canopy adventure', NULL, NULL, '1'),
